headline: Nvidia earnings highlighting AI demand could lift these stocks
summary: Ahead of Nvidia's first quarter earnings report, Rational Equity Armor Fund portfolio manager Joe Tigay joins Morning Brief with Brad Smith and Madison Mills to discuss which artificial intelligence (AI) sub-sector plays could react to the chipmaker's results. Tune in to Yahoo Finance's special live coverage of Nvidia's first quarter earnings here, beginning at 4:15 p.m. on Wednesday, May 28. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Morning Brief here.
